1) Pay court costs;
2) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
3) maintain fulltime employment or work search;
4) AODA assessment and follow through;
5) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
6) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
7) Provide DNA sample and pay the surcharge;
8) no contact with Corey Bowe, Brandi Arthur and Inman Jewelers;
9) Pay restitution of  $623.67 to Menards in Sheboygan, WI and $40.49 to Inman Jewelers;
